---
/**
 * BYOKExplainer — Prominent "Why BYOK?" section
 * Positions bring-your-own-API-key as a competitive advantage
 * Benefits: No Markup, No Lock-In, Free Tier, Cost Transparency
 */
---

<section id="byok" class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-text-primary text-balance mb-4">
        You Control the AI
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Connect your free AI account directly. No middleman. No markup. Full transparency.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Benefits Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Benefit 1: No Markup -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover" style="transition-delay: 0ms">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent-teal" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-semibold text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">No Markup</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Pay the AI service directly. We don't mark up costs. What they charge is what you pay.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 2: No Lock-In -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover" style="transition-delay: 50ms">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-orange/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent-orange" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-semibold text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">No Lock-In</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your account, your choice. Switch AI providers anytime. Not locked into QuickSay's infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 3: Free Tier -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent-teal" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-semibold text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">8 hrs/day Free</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          The free tier covers most users. Zero ongoing costs for typical usage. Heavy user? Upgrade for ~$3-5/month.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Callout -->
    <div class="fade-in-up bg-[#0e0e10] border border-accent-teal/20 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center" style="transition-delay: 150ms">
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-base leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Full cost transparency:</strong> You see exactly what you're using, exactly what it costs. No hidden fees, no surprise bills, no "contact sales" pricing tiers.
      </p>
      <a href="/download#groq-setup" class="inline-block mt-6 text-accent-teal hover:underline text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-150">
        Learn how to connect your account (2 minutes) →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
